{"tid":1463021,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"<幫手推!!!>癱瘓機場係致命武器!!!要好好利用!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:41.000Z","uid":274504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b970ea2e7119b29bd19487a6d9291bbe44c0d3d","tid":1463021,"uid":274504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"琴日既成果 係大部分客機都取消哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實証明的確係癱瘓到香港 呢個係政府既弱點!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時証明 響機場發夢係最安全的 沒有被狗咬沒有流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>點解安全?????</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">安全好緊要 我地已失去左太多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日有旅客響機場 一日機場都安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n睇番機場紀錄  雖然琴日下午6點後大部分離境機都取消<br />\n但其實6點後一直都有機到達香港  一直都有遊客出黎<br />\n甚至去到凌晨1-2點都會有不同既亞洲機到  得凌晨2-4點係真空期 (只有貨機)<br />\n到凌晨4-6點又會再安全  因為唔同國家既長途機會到香港  例如波士頓, 悉尼,西雅圖...<br />\n<br />\n1. 呢D長途要佢停飛 係要香港時間下午4,5 就要叫停<br />\n2. 起飛左 如果要停響第二個機場 政府係極低機會因為政治理由叫人降落另一個機場<br />\n一黎好多近香港既機場凌晨都不多人手 二黎飛機要考慮油飛去第二個機場<br />\n<br />\n所以政府好難控制機場既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記住一日有旅客響機場 一日機場都安全!!!!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢吹你唔脹 夠膽開坦克入黎 全世界幾多隻眼望住??!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解有用?????</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>宜家係無論幾多人出去夢遊 政府都可以吾理 所以夢岩地方好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n好多人平日要番工 好少時間訓<br />\n星期六日多D時間咪訓多D 發下夢囉<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最緊要人多 人多好緊要!</span></strong><br />\n一星期發到兩日夢 持續落去 效果一定比你想像中好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泰國當年反敗為勝 就係因為示威者封鎖出入國際機場的公路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知有人唔認同 因為會有短痛可能會影響遊客 會影響經濟<br />\n經濟起飛對你有受惠嗎? 長痛不如短痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs. 另外一個重點! 希望大家都留意到其實琴日貨機依然正常運行<br />\n貨機可以好影響到大公司既貨到 影響到大公司 佢地又點會唔出聲<br />\n好多貨機都係凌晨到港 機到都要經馬路既<br />\n馬路好危險! 貨唔到就大獲了!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fc48a50fb1280551b94af6f4870ded3eff6dc5","tid":1463021,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">weekend 一定夠人 好易塞爆 <br />\n8月17 18 齊齊塞機場啦 <br />\n星期六日 機場開唔到 迴響一定大<br />\n818 塞完再出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9819fe97fe326ee2e6e122148a27f34045ae3960","tid":1463021,"uid":274504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdd4be558955f6f2fc83002a74913e8de8317cfa","tid":1463021,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90a1fec92c2b04f91806a1657ffda041dcea7076","tid":1463021,"uid":274504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38cb9d7aeb34448a1d1184b28ae09d3b3f7ae04","tid":1463021,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"香港真正嘅弱點係進出機場嘅流量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463270</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e92f35cf5f60b1ade5c5d206bd84bf08fdfdf3ff","tid":1463021,"uid":274504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！"},{"pid":"af03cf0bd2a7ee694417e0e7b07e3e4a69cf57b6","tid":1463021,"uid":274504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}